                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900424-62-off333 t17900424-62-cd334"></join>, one watch, with a metal case, value 30 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17900424-62-victim576" type="victimName">
