                     <interp inst="t17900424-62-verdict336" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               GUILTY of stealing, not privately
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17900424-62-punish337" type="punishmentDescription">
